<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bʿd qryb jdạaⁿ yyjy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bʿd qryb jdaⁿạ yyjy .. yyjy ywm ạlạ̹kẖtṭạf
 ạstʿdwạ yạ mw̉mnyn .. dạ ạlrạʿy jạy llkẖrạf
 ạlqrạr- lạ tʿb wlạ ạ̉ḥzạn .. lạ bkạʾ wlạ dmwʿ
 (whạnskn mʿ ạlḥnạn .. ḥbyb ạlqlb yswʿ)2
 2- yạ mw̉mn ạnsy̱ ạlly fạt .. wạ̉nẓr ạ̹ly̱ ạlạ̉mạm
 wʿysẖ lly ʿsẖạnk mạt .. hạtqạbl rb ạlslạm
 3- dạ ạlwqt qṣyr wqlyl .. ạḥdẖr mn dnyạ ạlgẖrwr
 km lḥẓẗ wymr ạllyl .. wyṭlʿ fjr ạlsrwr
 4- ạ̉smạỷnạ mktwbẗ hnạk .. ʿndh fy sfr ạlḥyạẗ
 tʿạl wkẖdnạ mʿạk .. ạ̹mty̱ hạtyjy yạ ạbn ạllh</lyrics>
<hymn_number>431</hymn_number>
<author>fạyz bsẖry̱, fạyz bsẖry̱</author>
</song>